{"type": "article", "id": 18994, "title": "背带裤设计的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-14T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143616D36yqe7BT8PKbgGh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是瑞典的设计组合 Färg &amp; blanche 与瑞士家具品牌 johanson design 合作设计的椅子，灵感源于背带裤。从椅子后面可以看到三角结构将方形的靠背分割成了三块，是左右对称的，也很有几何感。椅子可以选择多种颜色并重叠放置，专门用在办公室等公共空间，是简单而注重功能性的北欧风格。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145717eETxOM0XVirpCq49.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"658\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80440098\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145717uzB4pyo8wQ13VEN0.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145717N2al6kSoePnxOCFW.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145718A64RLqHtV1PIfQ25.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}